== About
I am currently an algorithm engineer at [https://fabu.ai FABU.AI], focusing on solving decision-making and planning problems in autonomous driving from an optimization perspective. For further details, please refer to my [/cv.html CV].

== News
- May 2026: Our paper, "Accelerated Decentralized Constraint-Coupled Optimization: A Dual$^2$ Approach", is accepted by /IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing/.
- Aug. 2025: I rejoin FABU.AI as an algorithm engineer.
- Aug. 2025: I withdraw from my PhD at HKUST.
- May 2025: Our paper, "Accelerated Decentralized Constraint-Coupled Optimization: A Dual$^2$ Approach", is now available on [https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.03719 arXiv].
- May 2025: Our paper, "Dual Acceleration for Minimax Optimization: Linear Convergence Under Relaxed Assumptions", is now available on [https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.02115 arXiv].
- May 2025: Our paper, "Smoothness of the Augmented Lagrangian Dual in Convex Optimization", is now available on [https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.01824 arXiv].
- Aug. 2024: I start my PhD at HKUST.

